msgid "The PHP fallback runs PHP for every image (~50-200ms TTFB per image) versus ~5-20ms for static file serving. On an image-heavy page this compounds and can push Largest Contentful Paint past Google's 2.5s \"good\" threshold when an image is the LCP element — the difference between meeting and missing Core Web Vitals, not merely cosmetic."
