msgstr "Реплика (тайл)"

msgid "Smart"
msgstr "Smart"

msgid "<picture> element"
msgstr "Элемент <picture>"

msgid "Wrap eligible content images in a <picture> element with per-format <source> tags (AVIF/WebP) for progressive enhancement. Pro-gated (PICTURE_ELEMENT)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Wrap images in <picture> with per-format sources"
msgstr ""

msgid "When enabled, content <img> tags are wrapped in <picture><source type=\"image/avif\"><source type=\"image/webp\"><img></picture> for browser-negotiated format delivery."
msgstr ""

msgid "LQIP placeholders"
msgstr "LQIP-плейсхолдеры"

msgid "Low-quality image placeholders — tiny blurred previews via imgproxy that reduce Cumulative Layout Shift (CLS). Falls back to inline SVG when imgproxy is unreachable. Pro-gated (imgproxy-native)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Emit data-placeholder on img tags"
msgstr "Эмитить data-placeholder на img-тегах"

msgid "Blur sigma"
msgstr "Сигма размытия"

msgid "0.1–100. Higher = more blur. 1 is a good default."
msgstr "0.1–100. Больше = сильнее размытие. 1 — хороший default."

msgid "DPR-aware srcset"
msgstr "DPR-aware srcset"

msgid "For img tags with width but no srcset, generates 1x/2x/3x x-descriptor variants via imgproxy dpr: option. Images that already have w-descriptor srcset are left alone. Pro-gated (imgproxy-native)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Generate DPR variants for images without srcset"
msgstr "Генерировать DPR-варианты для изображений без srcset"

msgid "DPR multipliers"
msgstr "DPR-множители"

msgid "Comma-separated, 1–8. e.g. 1,2,3 for standard/retina/hyper-retina."
msgstr "Через запятую, 1–8. напр. 1,2,3 для standard/retina/hyper-retina."

msgid "Watermark"
msgstr "Watermark"

msgid "Applies imgproxy native watermark (wm: option). The watermark image is configured server-side via IMGPROXY_WATERMARK_PATH/URL — this setting controls placement only. Pro-gated (imgproxy-native)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Apply watermark"
msgstr "Применить watermark"

msgid "Opacity"
msgstr "Непрозрачность"

msgid "0 = transparent, 1 = opaque."
msgstr "0 = прозрачно, 1 = непрозрачно."

msgid "Position"
msgstr "Позиция"

msgid "X offset (px)"
msgstr "X-смещение (px)"

msgid "Y offset (px)"
msgstr "Y-смещение (px)"

msgid "Scale"
msgstr "Масштаб"

msgid "0 = auto-size, 0.1 = 10% of source image. Relative to source dimensions."
msgstr "0 = auto-size, 0.1 = 10% исходного изображения. Относительно размеров источника."

msgid "Failed to load diagnostics."
msgstr "Не удалось загрузить диагностику."

msgid "Failed to clear log."
msgstr "Не удалось очистить лог."

msgid "Off (silent)"
msgstr "Off (тихо)"

msgid "Basic (per-request counts)"
msgstr "Basic (счётчики на запрос)"

msgid "Verbose (per-URL with reason)"
msgstr "Verbose (по URL с причиной)"

msgid "Diagnostic level"
msgstr "Уровень диагностики"

msgid "Controls what gets written to the PHP error log on each page load. Off = no logging. Basic = one summary line per request (counts by context). Verbose = per-URL entries with reason + redacted source URL."
msgstr "Контролирует, что пишется в PHP error log при каждой загрузке страницы. Off = нет логирования. Basic = одна summary-строка на запрос (счётчики по context). Verbose = по-URL записи с причиной + редуцированным source URL."

msgid "Level"
msgstr "Уровень"

msgid "Changes take effect on the next page load. The admin bar item (frontend) shows live counts for the current page."
msgstr "Изменения вступят в силу при следующей загрузке страницы. Элемент admin bar (frontend) показывает live-счётчики для текущей страницы."

msgid "Cache size cap"
msgstr ""

msgid "Maximum disk space the LocalBackend image cache may use before the janitor evicts oldest entries. The janitor runs for everyone (disk safety); only the cap control is Pro. Under free, the default 512 MB cap is enforced."
msgstr ""

msgid "Cache cap (MB)"
msgstr ""

msgid "0 disables eviction (unlimited). Default 512. The janitor cron runs regardless — this only controls the cap."
msgstr ""

msgid "Recent log entries"
msgstr "Недавние записи лога"

msgid "Recent diagnostic entries from the last few requests. Entries are kept for 1 hour. Source URLs are redacted (host + truncated path only). Pro-gated (ADMIN_STATUS)."
msgstr ""

msgid "The active delivery status is shown at the top of this page. Detailed per-URL diagnostics are available on Pro."
msgstr ""

msgid "Loading…"
msgstr "Загрузка…"

msgid "Refresh"
msgstr "Обновить"

msgid "Clearing…"
msgstr "Очистка…"

msgid "Clear log"
msgstr "Очистить лог"

msgid "level: "
msgstr "уровень: "

msgid "Diagnostics are off. Set a level above and save to start logging."
msgstr "Диагностика выключена. Установите уровень выше и сохраните, чтобы начать логирование."

msgid "No entries yet. Visit a frontend page with images to generate log entries."
msgstr "Записей пока нет. Откройте frontend-страницу с изображениями, чтобы сгенерировать записи."

